                        <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left;">Gates concluded by asking the graduates what they see themselves accomplishing post-graduation.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left;">&ldquo;I can&rsquo;t wait to see what you do,&rdquo; she said.</p>
